  "title": "Dishwasher / Kitchen Steward",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us</strong></p><p>Chip Bee Bistro is a new casual-dining concept by High Note Hospitality Group. We’re a space for warmth, creativity, and genuine connections—built on authenticity, artistic curiosity, and old-school hospitality meets grown-up bistro life.<br /><br /><strong>What We're Looking For</strong></p><p>We are seeking a responsible and dedicated Dishwasher / Kitchen Steward to support daily kitchen operations. The successful candidate will play an important role in maintaining high standards of cleanliness and hygiene in the kitchen. This includes ensuring all dishes, utensils, and equipment are properly cleaned and sanitized, as well as providing basic assistance to the kitchen team when required.</p><p><strong>Role & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Wash, clean, and sanitize all dishes, glassware, utensils, and kitchen equipment to meet hygiene standards</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and proper organization of the dishwashing and kitchen areas to support efficient operations</li><li>Handle waste disposal by removing garbage and keeping waste areas clean and orderly</li><li>Comply with all food safety, hygiene, and workplace safety regulations to ensure a safe kitchen environment</li><li>Provide support for basic kitchen operations by assisting the kitchen team with assigned tasks as needed</li></ul><p><strong>What You Bring</strong></p><ul><li>Able to work in a fast-paced and dynamic environment</li><li>Physically fit and able to stand for extended periods during shifts</li><li>Demonstrate a positive attitude and strong teamwork skills to collaborate effectively with colleagues</li><li>Reliable and punctual with the ability to follow instructions and standard operating procedures accurately</li><li>Willingness to work on weekends and public holidays when required</li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li>Salary Range: $1,800 – $2,800</li><li>5-day work week (44 hours per week)</li><li>Discretionary year-end bonus</li><li>Group medical and hospitalization coverage</li><li>Staff discount</li><li>Staff meal provided</li></ul><p></p>",
